    "# ⚙️ Syndicate 3.0: Phase 7.5 Playroom (The Attention Engine)\n",
    "\n",
    "How do transformers dynamically shift focus across a sequence of words? They do not rely on static rules. They use **Scaled Dot-Product Attention**.\n",
    "\n",
    "In this playroom, you will master the raw linear algebra behind attention: Matrix transpositions, Matrix multiplications, and the math of the scaling factor that prevents gradients from vanishing during training, using **pure Python primitives**.\n",
    "\n",
